content.rendered:
Directed by Radha Krishna Jagarlamudi.

Written by Rajat Arora. Rajat Arora. D.S. Kannan.

Cast Akshay Kumar(Prof. Aditya Singh Rajput / Gabbar). Shruti Haasan(Shruti (as Shruti K. Haasan)). Kareena Kapoor(Sunaina Singh Rajput). Suman(Digvijay Patil). Sunil Grover(Constable Sadhuram). Jaideep Ahlawat(CBI Officer Kuldeep Pahwa). Ishita Vyas(Veena). Raj Singh Arora(Govind). Shruti Bapna(Lakshmi). Ravi Prakash(Ravi). Manoj Chandila(Vikas Patil). Vikas Shrivastav(Inspector Vikas). Fareed Ahmed(Parvesh). Anuradha Chandan(Govind’s mother). Jehangir Karkaria(Comic Doctor of Patil Hospital). Narendra Jetley(Senior Doctor). Jitendra Trehan(Dr. Manoj Verma). Afreen(Isha Dutta). Kumud Shaw(Dr. Kumud). Uday Atroliya(Collector). Jagdish Rajpurohit(Sub Inspector Yadav). Shivraj Walvekar(Police Commissioner Pant). Rajeev Kacho(Vishwas Sawant). Anandeshwar Dwivedi(News Reader). Uttam Halder(Ward Boy). Krishna Raaz(Shanti Nagpal). Prateek Srivastava(Hari). Boloram Das(Peon). Chandraprakash Thakur(Police (as Chandra Prakash Thakur)). Pradeep Shukla(Home Minister). Deepak Dadhwal(National College Principal). Ruby Parihar(Varsha). Robin Chaudhary(Taxi driver). Ashish Gokhale(Ajay). Sanjay Gurbaxani(Corrupt collector). Rajiv Kachroo(Inspector Vishwas Sawant). Anil Kumar(Taxi Driver). Harmanpreet Kaur(Nurse #1 in Patil Hospital). Anil Rai Mani(Bald Gangster at National College). Hetal Puniwala(Editor in Chief). Anoop Puri(Shruti’s boss). Rajiv Ranjan(Aditya’s friend). Sai Ballal(Corrupt Police officer). Pravina Bhagwat Deshpande(Govind’s mother). Chitrangda Singh(Item number) . Samir Chandra(Government Clerk).Deepjyoti Das. Kaluram Dhobale(CID Officer). Mahmood Hashmi(Hawaldar). Parth Ketkar(Ramesh (College Student)).Parihar Ruby. K K Shukla(Govt. Officer)

Language Hindi.

Producers Sanjay Leela Bhansali. Vicky Bhatia. Chetan Deolekar. Arvinder Gill. Gayatri Gulati. Shabinaa Khan. Smith Mehta. Yogiraj Shetty. Sandeep Singh. Ravinder Thakur.

Production Bhansali Productions. Viacom18 Motion Pictures.
